Wargówko  is a settlement in the administrative district of Gmina Czarna Dąbrówka, within Bytów County, Pomeranian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  north-west of Czarna Dąbrówka,  north of Bytów, and  west of the regional capital Gdańsk.
